description: Stunning RARE PENTHOUSE unit with soaring high ceilings on the 10th floor nestled in one of Boston's most coveted neighborhoods! State-of-the-art Fitness Center featuring Pelotons as well as high-end amenities such as top-notch concierge services, secure entry with valet parking, pet spa and a Club Room. Amazing common roofdeck offering spectacular panoramic city views, comfortable seating, dining setups, grills and a cozy fireplace. Wolf Stove,Subzero refrigerator, Quartz countertops and numerous high end cabinets make up your dream oversized kitchen! The unit features hardwood floors, alcove with room for office setup, a custom walk-in closet, in-unit laundry and central air. Located where South Boston meets Seaport, Broadway MBTA and just a short walk over bridge  to the South End, Whole Foods at Ink Block/SOWA area.  Best full service value in Boston! EMBRACE A  LIFESTYLE WHERE CUTTING-EDGE DESIGN AND CONVENIENCE ALIGN!
